org.locationtech.geowave.core.store.ingest

Class LocalPluginFileVisitor<P extends LocalPluginBase,R>

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.locationtech.geowave.core.store.ingest.LocalPluginFileVisitor<P,R>
  • Type Parameters:
    P - the type of the plugin
    R - the type for intermediate data that can be used throughout the life of the file recursion
    All Implemented Interfaces:
    FileVisitor<Path>

    public class LocalPluginFileVisitor<P extends LocalPluginBase,R>
extends Object
implements FileVisitor<Path>
    This class is used by any local file driver to recurse a directory of files. It will provide the plugin with any supported file with the appropriate extension within a directory structure.
